### Get all games
GET http://localhost:3000/games

###

### Create a game
POST http://localhost:3000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim",
  "genre": "Role-Playing",
  "platform": "PC",
  "releaseYear": 2011,
  "developer": "Bethesda Game Studios",
  "rating": 9,
  "multiplayer": false
}

###

### Get one game
GET http://localhost:3000/games/REPLACE_WITH_GAME_ID

###

### Update a game
PUT http://localhost:3000/games/REPLACE_WITH_GAME_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim",
  "genre": "Role-Playing",
  "platform": "PC",
  "releaseYear": 2011,
  "developer": "Bethesda Game Studios",
  "rating": 10,
  "multiplayer": false
}

###

### Delete a game
DELETE http://localhost:3000/games/REPLACE_WITH_GAME_ID

###

### Get all developers
GET http://localhost:3000/developers

###

### Create a developer
POST http://localhost:3000/developers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bethesda Game Studios",
  "country": "United States",
  "foundedYear": 2001,
  "website": "https://bethesdagamestudios.com"
}

###

### Get one developer
GET http://localhost:3000/developers/REPLACE_WITH_DEVELOPER_ID

###

### Update a developer
